CatDescriptText: Related images published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, January 9, 1960, pg. A9, reads: "D.I.'s Stage Another Triumph At Arena"
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Ruby Young Buchanan wearing full length long sleeved satin gown with wide waistband and imprinted floral vine pattern and dark fur stole over left shoulder, posing in interior for the D.I.'s National Foundation benefit, Margaret Watson standing on right
